Definition: aware or expressing awareness of things as they really are
Example: a realistic description; a realistic view of the possibilities; a realistic appraisal of our chances; the actors tried to create a realistic portrayal of the Africans
Synonyms: noun, person, realist, UNREALISTIC, POSSIBLE, PRACTICAL, REAL, aware, or, expressing, awareness, of, things, as, they, really, are, a, realistic, description, view, the, possibilities, appraisal, our, chances, actors, tried, to, create, portrayal, Africans
Category: adj.all
